    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p><p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p>",
