    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
