    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chicken breast </strong>and <strong>diced chorizo </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until golden</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1715959341278-x200.jpg",
