    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once golden, add the <strong>diced</strong> <strong>onion</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground smoked</strong> <strong>paprika</strong> and 2/3 of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> (save the rest for later!) with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
