      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>stock</strong> with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken & chorizo pie filling</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>chicken & chorizo pie filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and top with the <strong>crushed</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> (reserve the pot!)</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-18 min or until golden – this is your <strong>chicken & chorizo potato-topped pie</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
