    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken & chorizo potato-topped pie</strong> with the <strong>green</strong> <strong>beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>smoky saffron butter</strong> and garnish with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>parsley</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave off the smoky saffron butter and chopped parsley or just add a little!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
